{"tid":1715880,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解打仗要舉旗","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T07:57:37.000Z","uid":294765,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfba1154b8592622301c577a915e5dc3429dbd4","tid":1715880,"uid":294765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"琴日暴大一役打得非常漂亮<br />\n<br />\n一路見到有手足無停過fing支光復旗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OxYWZxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOxYWZxJ.jpg&h=0f235965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實有原因<br />\n<br />\n［古代的時候打仗，還有一個特別重要的東西，就是軍旗。衝鋒的時候需要專門的人扛，城池上也會插上，一看旗子，就知道這是誰的地盤。」<br />\n<br />\n手足們 proud of you!!!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b7f155f82f59c6e72652f77181e55c42bbd49c9","tid":1715880,"uid":158755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:54:12.000Z","msg":"一扯旗就好撚熱血，有無手足去音樂室拎埋鼓"},{"pid":"9e338758ba43bcd13f3fa89482f82b83c8e260fd","tid":1715880,"uid":14436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2ea10b2d0780ec6978afa58b5d27263690bbc9","tid":1715880,"uid":136149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"打仗最緊要士氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}